1. d4 Nf6 2. Nc3 d5 3. Bf4 c5
{ We shall conclude our survey of the Jobava Attack by examining this very thematic black option. }
4. e3 { The normal move. } 4... cxd4
{ The best move for Black. Other options are: } 5. exd4 a6 6. Nf3
{ At this point various moves have been tried: } 6... Bg4 7. h3 { Best; } 7...
Bxf3 { Better than } 8. Qxf3 Nc6 9. O-O-O e6 10. g4
{ The typical plan for White, after castling queenside, is to start a pawn storm on the kingside. However, since Black has not castled yet he has more options. }
10... Bb4
