1. d4 Nf6 2. Bf4 e6 3. e3 c5 4. c3 Nc6 5. Nf3 d5 6. Nbd2 Bd6
{ The alternative is 6... Be7, which we shall look at further on. } 7. Bg3
{ The normal response, with the idea of opening the h-file, if Black captures on g3, or playing f2-f4 in the future.   Black has also played }
