{ White sacrifices a second piece to open the h-file. } 14... fxg5 15. hxg5
{ and now: } 15... Rf5 16. Qh7+ Kf7 17. g6+ Ke8 18. Qxg7 Bf8 19. Rh8 Qe7 20.
Qh6 Kd8 21. g4 Kc7 22. gxf5 Bxh6 23. f6 Qc5 24. Bxh6 *

